{
  "texts": [
    "If a note contained any information on housing it had to be labeled as either stably housed, current housing instability, or history of/past housing instability.",
    "If the note contained no information on housing, it was labeled as unknown.",
    "These guidelines were then used to create the prompt used by the LLM.",
    "The annotation was divided into two rounds, with each reviewer annotating their own set of notes for the first round (original label).",
    "For the second round, 25% of the notes underwent dual annotation."
  ]
}